==Structure and protection==
*<code><event></code>: can have maximum protection.
**<code><event>/Info</code> and <code><event>/E-?</code>: should have low, moderate, or no protection.
**<code><event>/E-?/Enemy patterns</code> and <code><event>/E-?/Drop list</code>: in theory, can have maximum or at lest moderate protection, as it's generated and page comments can be used for feedback.
*Event templates can have some protection.

